{
  "stem": "7437.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was that-- the innocence and purity of these souls is, is with me to this day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I do feel that I owe them a great debt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this is to speak out and to tell their story.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And these occurrences happened almost daily.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I also forgot to mention before that when we came into the ghetto, shortly afterwards, there was a Judenrat formed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "A Judenrat was a group of men, not mostly, but all men, who were our intermediaries with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The Germans, it was beneath them to talk to a Jew, so they had the committee people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And all their requests came through the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Now, the Judenrat had a terribly difficult task because they had to deliver everything the Germans requested.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they had to deliver workers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Some of them were never seen again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And who and how to choose was a very difficult task.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this, this Judenrat stayed with us until the very end.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Now, life in the ghetto was getting from bad to worse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Morale was sagging, and people were getting desperate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But somehow, we continued.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "In my own personal case, I felt still protected by my older sister and by my mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And somehow, having their love and their caring kept me going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "This went on until the next spring.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And that, that was 1942.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "As spring came, our population, the numbers, dwindled.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There were probably half of the people in the ghetto at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the Germans decided we had too much space.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And so they moved us to an, an-- a smaller ghetto, which was at another part of town, also dilapidated and old.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, that part of town wasn't occupied for several years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "There were houses in great disrepair.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
